Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located within close proximity to US 31, directly connected to “class A” roads and  served by rail.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The complex is situated on over 400 acres at 1740 Whitehall Rd. Muskegon MI, the complex was originally built in 1975 with multiple additions  / renovations since, the latest being in 2016. The property is zoned IP – Industrial Park district. The plant is situated on a fenced 40 acre section of the property and has one active production plant and sits adjacent to a second non-active production plant and 13 support buildings, consisting of office, warehouse and tremendous in place infrastructure. The total square footage is approximately 168,000 square feet spread over the multiple buildings and floors.
